defaultTaxis could be used as an important part of the transport mix in addressing the needs
default of passengers in isolated communities. For instance if taxis are used to provide a failsafe option as part of a car sharing scheme
default 
default(e.g. through taxi vouchers or similar) then they could have a useful role to play. Similarly a web-based live portal for ta
defaultxi operators to use to advertise ‘dead’ journeys may also be useful in advertising journey opportunities / bring down journey costs for passengers.
defaultDemand responsive transport (DRT) services will only become cost effect
defaultive (to both commissioners and users)
default if they are widely used. This will only come about if they are marketed extremely well and the law around pre-booking these services is relaxed. 
default 
defaultOtherwise the cost of providing these services as things currently stand is likely to lead to their demise.
default&#xa0;defaultThe main challenges are related to the fact that there are fewer passengers available to be carried and often th
defaultey are spread over a larger geographical area than in urban areas.
